Package: BioTokenizeR
Type: Package
Title: Biology-aware Byte-pair Encoding (BPE) Tokenizer for biological sequences
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Sophia", "Li",
                  email = "sophiamjia.li@mail.utoronto.ca",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Sophia Li <sophiamjia.li@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: BioTokenizeR is an R package for tokenizing biological sequences
    (DNA, RNA, and proteins) by providing tools for generating, analyzing, and
    visualizing biologically meaningful tokens. It aims to be the first R 
    package to incorporate biological annotations into its byte-pair encoding
    (BPE) (Sennrich et al., 2016) merge strategy.
